WorkItem.Description:
The damage of Ferocious Bite is adjusted twice for the amount of CPs used.
 
The first adjustment lowers the amount of Bites that are done to compensate for biting with lower CPs:
float biteDamageMultiplier = Math.Min(1f, 
     (BiteStats.DamagePerSwing + BiteStats.DamagePerSwingPerCP * averageBiteCP) /
     (BiteStats.DamagePerSwing + BiteStats.DamagePerSwingPerCP * 5f));
biteCount += bitesFromAvailableCP * biteDamageMultiplier;
 
The second adjustment lowers the damage per bite when a lower amount of CPs is used:
float biteDamageTotal = biteCount * (BiteStats.DamagePerSwing + BiteStats.DamagePerSwingPerCP * biteCP);
